{"tid":724492,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"過咗咁耐 原來我最放唔低都係你","createTime":"2018-07-01T03:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T03:46:52.000Z","uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e752cd1719bc5381ec605b12ec67c476ff28022a","tid":724492,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"或者唔會再遇到一個你咁嘅人 原來之後鍾意嘅人只係為咗代替你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n亦都好彩我無因為咁害到其他人 但我以後都係自己一個比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bab5d4fa812a448f17c84cff277bd4ffb705df","tid":724492,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"為何永遠放不低　為何錯愛這一位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db88c548908f5f1b524d0a80417e58f731bd7a63","tid":724492,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"深呼吸　用腳寫日記　要去哪裡好呢<br />\n我漫步在人海裡我的手也冷得要命<br />\n<br />\n分開後　又幾年後　以為痛都好了<br />\n但是只要是一下雨就像天又彈著鋼琴　彈的是你<br />\n<br />\n原來愛上寂寞　會怕去愛　害怕走　卻得往前走<br />\n已經忘了很久　每個鏡頭　那時候的我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遠遠地　車浪無聲離去　馬路上人少了<br />\n寂寞很美麗像一部沒有了字幕的電影　嗯....<br />\n<br />\n停了電　自己煮了麵　讓漆黑的世界佔領<br />\n未來怎麼樣都可以　可是屬於我的愛情　可會來臨<br />\n<br />\nOH...... 害怕走　卻得往前走<br />\n以前快樂的我　給消滅後　還剩下什麼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18歲鍾意嗰個人 真係會掛住一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abcaef22be345fe207122832a6c0040297e9f4a","tid":724492,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到返返嚟啦好無"},{"pid":"aa64c20e9d609b5374c1a97c1d6654016156952f","tid":724492,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"最後一次見你 或者係幾個月之後畢業禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過也始終 不夠時間..."}]}